HIERARCHY PRINCIPLES:
â€¢ Headlines dominate with 40-60px font sizes
â€¢ Supporting text uses 16-18px with lighter color weight
â€¢ CTAs maintain consistent sizing but vary in visual prominence
â€¢ Metrics and proof points anchor credibility without competing for attention
â€¢ White space increases as content depth increases


